    • Field Detail

      • below

        @Option
public String below
        Determines if the layer will be inserted before the layer with the specified ID. If omitted or set to '', the layer will be inserted above every existing layer.

      • circle_radius

        @Option(value="circle.radius")
public Integer circle_radius
        The circle radius. Has an effect only when "type" is set to CIRCLE.

        Default: 15

      • color

        @Option
public String color
        The primary layer color. If "type" is CIRCLE, color corresponds to the circle color. If "type" is LINE, color corresponds to the line color. If "type" is FILL, color corresponds to the fill color If "type" is SYMBOL, color corresponds to the icon color.

        Default: "#444"

      • fill_outlinecolor

        @Option(value="fill.outlinecolor")
public String fill_outlinecolor
        The fill outline color. Has an effect only when "type" is set to FILL.

        Default: "#444"

      • line_width

        @Option(value="line.width")
public Integer line_width
        The line width. Has an effect only when "type" is set to LINE.

        Default: 2

      • opacity

        @Option
public Double opacity
        The opacity of the layer.

        Constraints: ≥0 and ≤1

      • source

        @Option
public String source
        The source data for this layer. Source can be either a URL, a geojson object (with "sourcetype" set to "geojson") or an array of tile URLS (with "sourcetype" set to "vector").

      • sourcelayer

        @Option
public String sourcelayer
        Specifies the layer to use from a vector tile source. Required for "vector" source type that supports multiple layers.

      • sourcetype

        @Option
public LayerOptions.SourceTypeEnum sourcetype
        The source type for this layer.

      • symbol

        @Option
public final SymbolOptions symbol
        Symbol options. Has an effect only when "type" is set to SYMBOL.

      • type

        @Option
public LayerOptions.TypeEnum type
        The layer type.

        Default: CIRCLE
